# Description: ESPHome subtree ignore policy for tracked project files.
# Version: 2026.04.18.1
# Last updated: 2026-04-18
#
# Repo policy: track ONLY control-py/, spectra_ls_system/, circuitpy/, packages/, and entrypoints.
# Ignore everything else by default.
*
!.gitignore
!control-board-esp32-tcp.yaml
!spectra_ls_system.yaml
!secrets.example
!control-py/
!control-py/**
control-py/previous/
control-py/previous/**
!spectra_ls_system/
!spectra_ls_system/**
spectra_ls_system/previous/
spectra_ls_system/previous/**
!circuitpy/
!circuitpy/**
!packages/
!packages/**

# Extra safety ignores (redundant with * but kept for clarity)
/.esphome/
/secrets.yaml
/control-py/secrets.yaml
/spectra_ls_system/secrets.yaml
/spectra_ls_system/.env
/spectra_ls_system/.esphome/
/control-py/.esphome/
control-py/previous/circuitpy/
.fseventsd/
.Trash-*/
.Trash-*
.metadata_never_index
.metadata_never_index:Zone.Identifier
.vscode/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
